### Queue Manager API Tests
### Base URL for the server
@baseUrl = http://localhost:9090

### Test 1: Create a queue message (Success case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/queue-manager
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "msg-001",
  "topic": "task-processing",
  "status": "CREATED"
}

### Test 2: Create another queue message with different topic
POST {{baseUrl}}/queue-manager
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "msg-002",
  "topic": "payments",
  "status": "processing"
}

### Test 3: Create queue message with completed status
POST {{baseUrl}}/queue-manager
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "msg-003",
  "topic": "notifications",
  "status": "completed"
}

### Test 4: Invalid JSON (Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/queue-manager
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "msg-004",
  "topic": "invalid"
}

### Test 5: Missing required fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/queue-manager
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "msg-005"
}

### Task Configuration API Tests

### Test 6: Create a TaskConfiguration (Success case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/configurations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startupDelay": 1000,
  "pollDuration": 5000,
  "topic": "task-processing",
  "fromStatus": "CREATED",
  "toStatus": "PICKED",
  "taskClass": "SampleTask",
  "task": "rO0ABXNyACNvcmcuZXhhbXBsZS5taW5pb24udGFza3MuU2FtcGxlVGFza3zMrPKfJRczAgABTAAHbWVzc2FnZXQAEkxqYXZhL2xhbmcvU3RyaW5nO3hwdAALU2FtcGxlIFRBU0s="
}

### Test 7: Retrieve a TaskConfiguration by taskClass
GET {{baseUrl}}/configurations/SampleTask
